\subsection{F\'ormulas de Conversi\'on}

Conversi\'on de MeV/cm$^3$ a Gray:
\formulabox{%
  D\,[\mathrm{Gy}] = D\,[\mathrm{MeV/cm}^3] \times 1.6 \times 10^{-13} \times \tau \times \mathrm{Actividad} \times 1000
}

Dosis Biol\'ogicamente Efectiva (BED):
\formulabox{%
  \mathrm{BED} = D + \frac{\lambda}{(\alpha/\beta)(\lambda + \mu)} \cdot D^2
}

Dosis Uniforme Equivalente (EUD):
\formulabox{%
  \mathrm{EUD} = \left( \sum_i v_i \cdot D_i^a \right)^{1/a}
}

Dosis Equivalente en Fracciones de 2 Gy (EQD2):
\formulabox{%
  \mathrm{EQD2} = \frac{\mathrm{BED}}{1 + \frac{2}{\alpha/\beta}}
}

